Bardic Inspiration
You can inspire others through stirring words or music. A creature can add the inspiration die to one ability check, attack roll, or saving throw.

Jack of All Trades
You can add half your proficiency bonus, rounded down, to any ability check you make that doesn't already include your proficiency bonus.
